      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for someone who doesn't mind a bit of a fixer-upper! While it shows significant signs of its journey and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring some life back into a classic commuter. An honest car at an honest price!",
