      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in peerless condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering is intended for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
