      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and has been loved every mile of the way, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine's high-pressure VANOS system has been meticulously overhauled, and the individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous transient throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Crucially, the rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement have been completed, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a precise short-throw six-speed manual transmission. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior free of bolster wear, this vehicle retains its original suspension geometry and kinematic balance, delivering the pure, communicative driving experience synonymous with the M division\u2019s golden era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. Full service records. No cosmetic or mechanical flaws. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-ready condition, this vehicle is a preserved example for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied from day one; there are no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing rain or snow. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, organized binder of documentation included. The engine bay is meticulously clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
