      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal are beyond reproach, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail has been meticulously preserved to ensure an uncompromising driving experience.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
